 Orange 11 2/3, Brea-Olinda 9 1/3 -- Josh O'Neill won at No. 1 singles, 6-3, 
6-4, 6-4, and Alfred Gomez and Jason Wang won at No. 1 doubles, 6-2, 6-2, 6-2, 
for Orange (7-1). Brea-Olinda is 7-3. 
</P>
<P>
 Villa Park 13, Valencia 5 -- Ryan Hollis swept No. 1 singles, 6-1, 6-0, 6-0, 
B.K. Chang swept No. 2 singles, 6-0, 6-1, 6-0, and Paul Cho won two of three in 
No. 3 singles, 6-2, 6-3, 2-6, to lead Villa Park (8-1). 
</P>
<P>
 Western 13, Buena Park 8 -- Mack Sunthonlap swept in singles, 7-6, 6-1, 6-3, 
and Dean Ras and Danh Dao swept in doubles, 6-0, 7-6, 6-0, for visiting Western 
(3-5). Buena Park is 0-5. 
</P>
