<P>
 Karie Davies reached base on a bunt-single and later scored on catcher Liz 
Jones' error in the eighth inning to give Orange Coast a 1-0 victory over 
Riverside in an Orange Empire Conference softball game Wednesday at Orange 
Coast College. 
</P>
<P>
 Pirate pitcher Kelsi Armbruster pitched a one-hitter to pick up her 11th 
victory of the season.The victory moves the Pirates (15-8-2, 6-2 in conference) 
into second place. 
