</P>
<P>
 Thomas Davis, whose first book "Suffer Little Children" earned a Shamus Award, 
will sign "Murdered Sleep" at 1 p.m. Saturday at Mysteries to Die For, 2940 
Thousand Oaks Blvd., Thousand Oaks. 
</P>
