<P>
 South Korea placed its armed forces on special alert as the north warned that 
U.S. deployment of antimissile batteries in the south will push the peninsula 
to the brink of war. In another move likely to inflame the situation, the south 
said that this year's joint military exercises with U.S. forces will involve 
