<P>
 Numbers switched -- A Ventura County crime chart that ran Tuesday incorrectly 
listed thefts as auto thefts and vice versa.The numbers were switched for each 
of the 10 cities and countywide. The correct number of thefts countywide was 
15,868 for 1992 and 14,310 for 1993. The total number of auto thefts countywide 
was 2,757 for 1992 and 2,781 for 1993. 
